Welcome to East Scarp! 

An expansion adding new NPCs; new locations; new fish; shops; special orders - and secrets.

In a picturesque location by the sea.

Make the horse the way it should be, thin, fast and useful. Put items into its saddle bags, pet it and give it water and food to befriend your horse to increase its movement speed. 



Also includes a menu to check on horse or pet friendship and adds sound effects to the previously silent horse.
State.Name: Horse Overhaul - Thin - Faster - Saddle Bags - Friendship

State.Author: BPsysGamer
State.Description: Add a cellar to your cabin on the island
State.Name: Island Cellar

Original.Name: Juliet and Jessie the JojaMart Clerks-6398-1-4-6-1669936652.zip

State.Author: LemurKat
State.Description:
Juliet is a troubled young woman exiled to Pelican Town for reasons unknown, but possibly linked to her sharp-tongue and flirty, irrepressible nature. Her

co-worker, housemate, and friend, Jessie is matronly, empathic, and a keen gardener and herbalist.
State.Name: Juliet and Jessie the Joja Clerks

State.Author: aedenthorn
State.Description: Lets you purchase specific types of chicken and cow, including blue, void, and golden chickens.
State.Name: Livestock Choices

State.Author: Rafseazz
State.Description:
VISUAL OVERHAUL UPDATE!

Adds lots of new content! From custom NPCs to new locations to even more!!

Check description below!
State.Name: Lunna - Astray in Stardew Valley

State.Author: DecidedlyHuman
State.Description: This mod does nothing on its own. Its primary purpose is to allow map authors to spice up their maps with the new custom tile properties, extra features, etc., that this mod adds.
State.Name: Mapping Extensions and Extra Properties (MEEP)

Original.Name: Miss Coriel's NPC Unique Courtship Response 5-3312-5-0-0-1643035108.zip

State.Author: MissCoriel
State.Description: Tired of everyone responding with "...!! I'll accept this. Thank you." When you give them flowers?  Want them to accept your pendant in a way more to their character?  Want your custom NPCs to as well.. Then look no further!!
State.Name: MissCoriel's NPC Unique Courtship Response 4 - Happy Birthday

State.Author: ceruleandeep
State.Description: Tired of watching your Multiple Spouses smooching all the time? Ever wish they could take a break for like 2 minutes? Nah, me neither. But this mod at least gets them saying cute things in between snogging, pashing, and making out.
State.Name: Multiple Spouse Dialogs

State.Author: DestyNova
State.Description: Introducing the "swords" half of "swords and sorcery" to East Scarp! Befriend our resident rogue, Mateo, as they embark on their thrilling expedition into an all new era of adventures.
State.Name: Never Ending Adventure - NPC Mateo

State.Author: atravita
State.Description: Quick mod that (a) makes Penny's 8 heart event only happen on sunny days and (b) slightly alters it when you have children to to take into account the fact that I ALREADY HAVE KIDS, PENNY.
State.Name: Penny 8 Heart Event Adjusted

State.Description: Allows Pierre to sell Tree Fertilizer after the player reaches Foraging level 7.
State.Name: Pierre Sells Tree Fertilizer

State.Description: Makes the random name generator use realistic names based on predefined lists.

State.Description: Audio API & Audio Management for SMAPI, without the need for Harmony. Add custom audio tracks.

State.Name: Seasonal Outfits for Zinnia (Adventurer's Guild Expanded)

State.Description: A Framework mod that allows modders to add custom shops to the game, as well as edit vanilla shops. Unofficial update uploaded w/ permission from Cherry that adds wallpaper & floor support.
State.Name: Shop Tile Framework - UNOFFICIAL Wallpaper and Floor Update

State.Description: Adds additional possible required tags for special orders by monkeypatching SpecialOrder.CheckTag. Also adds some debugging tools.
State.Name: Special Orders Tags Extended

State.Author: Andrew Young
State.Description: Right-click with your watering can and watch yourself water your crops! Unlike other mods, the crops won't be instantly watered. Your farmer will go crop by crop watering them, expending the same amount of time and energy as if you had done it yourself to keep as vanilla as possible, but a lot less tedious!
State.Name: Water Bot

State.Author: Mineral Town Architects
State.Description: Welcome to the world and characters that inspired not only Stardew Valley, but fans of farming sims as a whole. With characters either familiar or brand new, expand your horizons in Mineral Town.
State.Name: Welcome to Mineral Town

State.Author: FloranceBless
State.Description:
Meet Wilford! He's quite an unusual person, but I'm sure you can find common ground.

What can an acquaintance with a lonely florist lead to? Find it out!
State.Name: Wilford - New Custom NPC

State.Author: Yagisan
State.Description: The valley becomes alive with a variety of new forage.
State.Name: Yagisan's Bountiful Valley

State.Author: Yri
State.Description: Adds a new architect to East Scarp. Lewis wants a better town? So someone needs to do the job right! Set a strong foundation to reach unprecedented heights, otherwise our precious home will crumble and fall. Robin needs a pay raise and Yri is here to deliver.
State.Name: Yri the Architect - New Custom NPC's for East Scarp

State.Author: SmolHooman
State.Description: Adds some wild animals to the game.
State.Name: (CC) SH's Wild Animals

State.Description: Updates and expands on an NPC named Alec, originally by HopeWasHere.
State.Name: Alec Revisited

State.Author: Khloe Leclair
State.Description: Almanac provides an in-game book with useful information about different subjects, including a long term weather forecast and when to plant crops.
State.Name: Almanac

State.Author: DaLion
State.Description: Makes Fish Ponds useful and immersive by preserving fish quality, scaling roe production with population, and spontaneously growing algae if left empty.
State.Name: Aquarism - Immersive Fish Ponds

State.Author: atravita
State.Description: A collection of little tweaks: don't pick up rugs if there's something on them! Place grass under things! Confirmation on bomb placement! Right click the butterfly hutch to spawn more butterflies! Gates no longer randomly pop off!
State.Name: Atras Interaction Tweaks - aka Stop Rug Removal

State.Author: Pathoschild
State.Description: Place a chest next to a machine (like a furnace or crystalarium), and the machine will automatically pull raw items from the chest and push processed items into it. Connect multiple machines with a chest to link them.
State.Name: Automate

State.Author: Cat
State.Description: This mod makes jelly, pickles, wine, juice, and honey icons be based on the fruit, vegetable, or flower used to make them. Easily tell at a glance what types of wine, jelly, etc you have in your inventory! (You can hide the little icons if you want too :))
State.Name: Better Artisan Good Icons

State.Author: Hootless
State.Description: Framework to change the bus ticket machine into an easily extendable menu, allowing modders to add their own maps as a destination for the bus!
State.Name: BusLocations

State.Description: Access your chests, dressers, fridge, shipping bin, and Junimo huts from anywhere and organise them your way. Transfer items without having to run around, from the comfort of your bed to the deepest mine level. Includes optional balanced mode.
State.Name: Chests Anywhere

State.Description: Attach C# code snippets to your Content Patcher packs.

Tree colors are more varied and change gradually as the seasons change.



Uses Alternative Textures and Content Patcher.

State.Author: Goldenrevolver
State.Description:
Make the horse the way it should be, thin, fast and useful. Put items into its saddle bags, pet it and give it water and food to befriend your horse to increase its movement speed. 



Also includes a menu to check on horse or pet friendship and adds sound effects to the previously silent horse.

Jade is a self-proclaimed entomologist, lover of all things magical, and generally an odd person to meet.

Fully romanceable and marryable. Can you figure out this odd girls secrets?

State.Description:
Jas is a lonely child, with only Vincent to play with, and the two adults in her life having little time with her, so what she needs is an animal friend.



Introducing, Mister Ginger!



Now in English, Chinese, Korean, Russian, Portugese

(not all portions 100% translated due to updates)

State.Description: See NPC and players on the map, with an optional minimap.

State.Description: After becoming the laughing stock of his peers for his 'outrageous' theories regarding the dwarves, geologist Professor Jasper Thomas has returned to Pelican Town.  Can you help him overcome his embarrassment? Or will he fall prey to his obsession?
State.Name: Professor Jasper Thomas

State.Description: A Remote Villa Farm on a hill, in a forest, with a private beach.
State.Name: Remote Villa Farm

Compatible with Windows, Linux, and MacOS.

State.Name: Chelsea - New Custom Datable NPC

This mod adds 51 types of pizza to the game, using vanilla ingredients, all of which have gift tastes for vanilla characters. Each villager has at least one pizza they love. It also adds "Pizza Base", an item I created, to act as a base for most of the pizzas.

Please download the newest version for the mod to work.

State.Author: tiakall
State.Description: Jean demands full rights for Joja workers! Jorts is stuck in a trashcan. Classic Jorts! They're cats, they talk, and now they're new custom NPCs in your game.
State.Name: Jorts and Jean the Helper Cats - New Custom NPCs

State.Name: Lavril - East Scarp NPC (King's Raid)

State.Author: Zoedoll
State.Description: Pika's wife and Keahi's mother from Ridgeside Village!
State.Name: Leilani (NPC for Ridgeside Village)

Original.Name: Lumisteria Toddlers Like Parents - Alternative Children-10494-1-0-0-1641071257.zip

The obelisk will be miniaturized to improve visibility.

Floors can also be changed in detail.

There is also the appearance of the season.

RSV, ES, DTZ, DWM, SWO (Custom Obelisks), can also be set.
